		section.faq

			.faq-heading--box
			
				h3.faq-heading.section__heading-underline Frequently Asked Questions
				
			.faq-text--box
				.faq-text--box-item
				
					.faq-text--box-q
						strong How much does a website usually cost?
					.faq-text--box-a
						p Pricing depends on what the business needs, but every project is quoted clearly before work begins.
						
				.faq-text--box-item
					.faq-text--box-q
						strong How long does a website take to build?
					.faq-text--box-a
						p Smaller websites can often be completed within a few weeks, while larger or more custom projects can take longer.
						
				.faq-text--box-item
					.faq-text--box-q
						strong Do I need to have everything ready before getting started?
					.faq-text--box-a
						p No. You do not need to have everything figured out first. We can work through what is needed step by step.

				.faq-text--box-item
					.faq-text--box-q
						strong Can you help with updates after launch?
					.faq-text--box-a
						p Yes. Ongoing support is available before and after launch, including updates, fixes, and general help.
						
				.faq-text--box-item
					.faq-text--box-q
						strong Do you only work with Bundaberg businesses?
					.faq-text--box-a
						p Widebay Web Wise is based in Bundaberg and works with businesses across the Wide Bay region.
							
					
		section.portfolio
		 
			.portfolio-heading--box
			
				h3.portfolio-heading.section__heading-underline Recent Projects
			
				p A look at recent website builds and current projects.
				
			.portfolio-grid
			
			
